sources.title: Doped Youth (1936) Reefer Madness
sources.description:
Stars: Dorothy Short, Kenneth Craig, Lillian Miles 
Director: Louis J. Gasnier

Rare alternate titled version of the classic Reefer Madness. In this highly fictionalized tale, a trio of drug dealers lead innocent teenagers to become addicted to "reefer" cigarettes by holding wild parties with jazz music.
